sorry to reply a litte bit late. Before I give my unit test code, I want to introduce our sharding algrothmn.
we have a table, named business_info, so we create java bean, mapper(dao). 
And we based on businessNo to get sharding table name. for example, businessNo is 330108002-0017-0118, so sharding table is business_info_330108002, it is simple. But becasue we may have some like query opreation. so we use Hint router to do like operation. Regarding it, we use special flag to distinct which we should give all table, which we give related table.
```
case1: use alltable mean get all sharding tables.
HintManager hintManager2 = HintManager.getInstance();
hintManager2.addDatabaseShardingValue("business_info", "businessNo", "database");
hintManager2.addTableShardingValue("business_info", "businessNo", "alltable");

case2: use alltable:level1 mean we get related sharding tables
HintManager hintManager2 = HintManager.getInstance();
hintManager2.addDatabaseShardingValue("business_info", "businessNo", "database");
hintManager2.addTableShardingValue("business_info", "businessNo", "alltable:level1");
