SHOW {INDEX | INDEXES | KEYS}
          {FROM | IN} tbl_name
          [{FROM | IN} db_name]
          [WHERE expr]

2. You can use db_name.tbl_name as an alternative to the tbl_name FROM db_name syntax. These two
